## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-141">如果您调用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>并且没有任何文档导航返回到<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>不会执行一个导航和引发异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-141">If you call <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> and there are not any documents to navigate back to, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> does not perform a navigation and an exception is thrown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-142">如果需要可以检查的值<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>属性以确定是否要向后定位到的文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-142">If you need to, you can inspect the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A> property to determine whether there are documents to navigate back to.</span></span>  
  
   
  
