## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> 不应调用之前加载完成后将其实现的文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-161">当文档加载完成后通过处理可以检测<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-161">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-162">下面的示例演示如何从文档中调用的脚本函数[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]应用程序使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-162">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-163">在此示例中，脚本函数没有任何参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-163">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-164">下面是[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]实现将从调用的脚本函数的文档[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-164">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-165">如下所示[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]实现来脚本函数中调用[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-165">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> 不应调用之前加载完成后将其实现的文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-174">当文档加载完成后通过处理可以检测<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-174">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-175">如果您要调用的脚本未通过足够多的参数值，不传递到值的参数将具有未定义的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-175">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-176">如果传递的参数值太多，将忽略多余的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-176">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-177">下面的示例演示如何通过使用，从应用程序调用脚本函数文档<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-177">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-178">在此示例中，脚本函数需要参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-178">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-179">以下是实现将从调用的脚本函数的文档[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-179">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-180">如下所示[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]实现来调用脚本中的函数[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-180">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-194">调用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>具有相同的效果与设置<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-194">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> 由开发人员想要以声明方式指定的初始文档的使用，根据标记<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>导航到时<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>初始化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-196">使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29>方法以导航到可能包括转义符的 URL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-197">使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>方法可导航到<xref:System.Uri>，不包括转义符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-197">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-198">下面的示例演示如何使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>通过使用来导航到文档<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-198">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-216">使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29>方法以导航到可能包括转义符的 URL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-216">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-217">使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29>方法可导航到<xref:System.Uri>，不包括转义符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-217">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-218">下面的示例演示如何导航到文档并在新的浏览器窗口中将其打开，通过指定"有关： 空白"目标。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-218">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-229">如果`stream`参数是`null`，<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>导航到空白文档 ("有关： 空白")。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-229">If the `stream` parameter is `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to a blank document ("about:blank").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-230">如果流参数不在有效[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]格式，它将以明文形式显示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-230">If the stream parameter is not in a valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, it will be displayed as plain text.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-231">在导航窗格中之后,<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>将为`null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-231">After navigation, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> will be `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6f6fa-232">下面的示例演示如何导航到包含文档的流。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6f6fa-232">The following example shows how to navigate to a stream that contains a document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateToStreamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Load HTML document as a stream  
  Uri uri = new Uri(@"pack://application:,,,/HTMLDocumentWithScript.html", UriKind.Absolute);  
  Stream source = Application.GetResourceStream(uri).Stream;  
  
  // Navigate to HTML document stream  
  this.webBrowser.NavigateToStream(source);  
}  
```

  
  
